{"tid":1550886,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[深藍]不如整個平台，大家一齊紀錄警察每日Highlight&MVP事跡","createTime":"2019-09-07T18:24:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T00:27:03.000Z","uid":293921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"aa86f96c13629dfd087a891e3a8a1e64e7bdb169","tid":1550886,"uid":293921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:24:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">其實警察都好辛勞，每日都要千變萬化既事要佢地去沖出黎同市民沖突，不過每日發生既事太多，有無IT狗可以幫手整返個平台紀錄佢地每日英勇事跡，警示一下市民，等佢地無方法狡辯？另外都讚揚警方每日既功勞？</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><br />\n<strong>個平台應該是咁，等各界都可以一齊加入資料，令事實還原。</strong><br />\n<strong>１有分類</strong><br />\n按日子及警察種類（特種警察部隊，高級警員等）、行為（武力制服，鉛袋彈，警告記者等）分類搜尋<br />\n<br />\n<strong>２有證據</strong><br />\n所有紀錄需要有證據（影片、相片、口述等）（純文字就另一類別作參考），而所有證據需上載至第三方伺服器（最好係Blockchain）<br />\n<br />\n<strong>３有人手有透明</strong><br />\n由於太多人做證，個平台應該有兩個版本，一個係人手認證紀錄（要人手睇圖文相符），一個係電腦認證紀錄（填曬所有資料就可以刊登），人手既就準確度高，電腦既就透明度高。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">例如如下 - (係其中一個有力證據，警察努力維護社會安寧)<br />\n07/09/2019 - 防暴警察 - 警告市民<br />\n兩名防暴警在旺角道巴士站趕走等待巴士的乘客，要脅將其拘捕。一名男乘客挺身而出，三人唇槍舌劍，當男乘客表示他有律師時，防暴警於半秒內敗走<br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/wod4k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fwod4k&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC9eKooxOH8zUMv7fiy4eq7s%3D&h=021961ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/wod4k</a></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>如果有人肯整就好啦，請IT狗出動，令事實環原</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"a94a4b2c2b7432d27d6c93b3f45c232778385458","tid":1550886,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:24:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f2eae88015f95f940ffa10e7659814078981346c","tid":1550886,"uid":232167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:24:44.000Z","msg":"熱門一個908嘅post都冇？入嚟推兩野<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1550800\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1550800</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5dfa3e6818eb912c98faac256514af1faa6e369c","tid":1550886,"uid":258566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:29:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8fa7ef09985bf9dda8f26fc826204b8982cda78f","tid":1550886,"uid":268959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:34:11.000Z","msg":"隔離po有片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4293cdb3d9a7fe3c5d97ecc0918b7ae76b5dab14","tid":1550886,"uid":293921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T19:00:00.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"3a07f92b435c1d5cceb0fa31631648bfb588f8a3","tid":1550886,"uid":293921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T02:02:22.000Z","msg":"點睇"},{"pid":"805a6894ef1c3e4ebb84d7900d2bd321eb288f0d","tid":1550886,"uid":293921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T00:40:07.000Z","ms